Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,射擊 還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,狙擊手是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,狙擊手是這樣
