Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:27.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,自分だけで決めた　可能性なんて　もう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.59,0:01:33.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,笑っちゃうくらい当てにならないから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:43.94,OPJP,,0,0,0,,閉じた眼で作り出していた  安全圈置いてけぼりにしていこう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:53.24,OPJP,,0,0,0,,未来がまだレティクルの  真ん中捉えられなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:01:57.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,顔を上げるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:02:00.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,いつもの場所も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.21,0:02:03.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,鈍色のルールも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:09.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,躓いても変えていくから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:14.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,手を取られながら　でも歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:21.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,足跡はたくさんの色で  あふれてるの
Comment: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:42.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:27.59,OPCH,,0,0,0,,獨自一人繪出的未來地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.59,0:01:33.22,OPCH,,0,0,0,,是那麼地朦朧 連自己都覺得可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:43.94,OPCH,,0,0,0,,捨棄那閉上眼所畫出的安全圈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:53.24,OPCH,,0,0,0,,即使未來仍在目鏡的中央飄忽不定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:01:57.00,OPCH,,0,0,0,,也要抬頭挺胸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:02:00.13,OPCH,,0,0,0,,無論是那一成不變的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.21,0:02:03.30,OPCH,,0,0,0,,還是那黯淡無光的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:09.01,OPCH,,0,0,0,,即使幾經挫折 也定能使其煥然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:14.97,OPCH,,0,0,0,,手牽著手 卻從未停下步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:21.90,OPCH,,0,0,0,,身後的足跡是那麼地五彩繽紛

Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:45.48,標題,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\be2\pos(948,583)}敵彈，連同靈魂一併射穿？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,這個賽場附近有個溫泉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 景色也不錯 露天浴場最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:57.04,註釋,,0,0,0,,自然湧出掘削自噴溫泉！\N距賽場徒步15分鐘，\N最近車站配有巴士接送。\N讓天然溫泉治癒你賽後疲憊的身體吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好 大家戴上標誌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:02:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,標誌？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,為了不弄混敵人和隊友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,每隊像這樣將標誌戴在胳膊上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,由良砰也戴上 來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\3c&HF7F7F7&\pos(640,38)\c&H646464&}今天的生存遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 趁現在來確認一下今天大賽的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的大賽是取得敵方陣地上的旗幟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,或者全殲敵人的一隊獲勝的奪旗戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是淘汰制哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,還有 由良良是第一次參加這樣大型的比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,把頭髮梳起來活動會更容易吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 確實是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不對 應該這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就決定用這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這才是最終髮型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,由良林
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,比起勉強梳起來 像現在這樣不也挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:03:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這個拜託啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:03:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,即將開始第一場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,參賽隊伍請到門口集合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好勒！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 奮命一搏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:14.99,註釋,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02}「当たって砕けろ」這句諺語的直譯是「撞上去粉身碎骨」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.72,0:04:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,粉身碎骨可怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…擊中並綻開…怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:20.62,註釋,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02}「当たる」也有擊中的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這個很有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 就這樣喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,C3部 一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,擊中並…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.15,0:04:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,綻開吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好緊張 我能打好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,旗幟由我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你就盡情地進攻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,5 4 3…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,手榴彈！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 旗幟我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,由良砰 前進啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在正面 這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,來掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,得手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,命中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,卡莉 真有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡唷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,卡莉拉在吸引對方 趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:05:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,由良良 前進
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,卡莉拉學姐被盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不對啦 由良良 卡莉拉是誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,命中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,太好啦！ 太好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 擊中你了 真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,靠…在給敵人道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,由良良 這是在比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,即便擊中了也不用這麼道歉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 總之戰果不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,三對一嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,命中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這個距離的話 即使是由良良也能奪到旗子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,前進！ 旗幟已經在眼前了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,旗幟…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 由我來奪合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這個人很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,前進吧 由良良
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我來給你當誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,小穂香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,前… 前進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,衝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,成功啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,搞不好我的生存遊戲出道戰幹得很漂亮耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,幹得好 由良林
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然也有beginner's luck的因素在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦好啦 也算有了不少的活躍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,作為第一次來說不是很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,比自己想像中更活躍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 下一場比賽馬上要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要補充好彈藥和水分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來是為時1小時的午休時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,呼…終於休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真漫長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然一場比賽只有15分鐘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺流了一年的汗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,果然 打完生存遊戲就要吃咖哩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很辣 但是很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,也請品嚐茶和點心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我看了對戰表
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,下一個對手是明星女子學園呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是支很強的隊伍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,與其說是強 不如說是呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,至今為止與她們交手過四次 但全是平手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一次也沒贏過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,其中 那位叫春奈凜的隊長 非～常強大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,春奈…凜…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,而且那個叫凜的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,還是小園在美國的生存遊戲搭檔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我也從來沒贏過她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙雖然很強 但是很沒勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,和那傢伙組隊什麼的 要是我的話絕對做不來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,春奈凜 到底是位怎樣的人呢……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我去裝些水來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 我也去！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我先去趟洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz5.855\frx8\fry354\move(560,103,502,97)}置物櫃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.519\move(577,437,515,448)}供水處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.93,0:10:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 非常抱歉 小園學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:10:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？好久不見？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,唷 這是我們的新部員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很可愛吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你也一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.03,0:11:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,無論過去 還是現在 亦或將來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不會原諒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？那… 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛那話是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這次的作戰 是從側面瞄準一點突破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,由全員進攻的閃電戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,閃… 閃電戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶 久違的進攻手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是符合C3部風格的作戰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,一般來講 應該是在旗幟前擺好陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,均衡分為進攻方和防守方的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,帶著身為新手的由良良 進行少數人作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,若以明星為對手 說實話勝面很小
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但是全員一起進攻的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就算被包圍也還有勝利的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,所以這次就以一點突破為方針進行速攻 以上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,看我一瞬間了結了她們！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,能做到嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,勝負乃兵家常事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,擊中並綻開 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我也要前進…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:12:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,由良公 你幹嘛呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,前進啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 敵人 有敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小卡莉 危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,命中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,小八
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,命中了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,小蓮也！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,由良良
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,別發呆 往前看！要上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.58,0:13:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,從側面的速攻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,照顧新人的同時所展開的總體戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,卡莉拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.35,0:14:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,命中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 對方差不多該來奪旗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,凜就由我來擋住 趕緊上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才說要我們趕緊上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不… 不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然要從這槍林彈雨中穿過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,再來得更猛烈些吧 園羅！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,由良良！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我的錯 都怪我錯過了時機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就連小園學姊也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪 明星應該很輕鬆就能奪下旗子才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的啊 不行的啊 只靠我一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,凜 斯特拉還剩下一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,奪下旗子結束這場比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 要結束了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要旗子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,把C3部一個不剩地消滅掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,還在找我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:15:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,必須逃走才行！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了 被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,投… 投降
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我棄權…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,結束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,由於斯特拉女學園C3部棄權
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,明星女子學園獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,啊勒？剛剛廣播說棄權了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,確實是這樣聽到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼沒有戰鬥到最後一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,毫無任何覺悟就來參與生存遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你的態度讓我很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是為了什麼在戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒有參與生存遊戲的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 凜 你在跟我們家由良公瞎說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不用在意那傢伙說的話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 還有下次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不用在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 小園你也說點什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:17:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,小園學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,凜說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,今天由良林糟蹋了同伴們的犧牲 自己一個人逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人就不能戰鬥的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,和大家在一起也一樣無法戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要笑到倒下的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,區區失敗不足為懼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,今天這樣的行為不許再有第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 總之
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,泡溫泉啦 溫泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,只有在這裡才能見到摘下眼鏡的小穗香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,裸體的小穗香學姊真的會讓人看入迷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然還有個完全沒有吸引力的小不點在就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,什～麼～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你說誰小不點啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:18:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,再說一遍看看！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,卡莉拉 不許跳進浴池
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,別這麼死板嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎麼辦才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,總之先付出行動啦 行動！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,只靠行動說話！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,看 拜此所賜得到了這麼多的勳章！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,由良良
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.15,0:19:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就算叫你不用在意今天的事 也是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所謂的不許再有下次 就是說還有一次機會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就是 不要太在意！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.69,0:19:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那個… 讓你們這麼為我操心 真是抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,糟蹋了同伴們的犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我本以為到了新的地方就會有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,進了C3部就一定能改變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 那只不過是推給他人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我在瞎誤會些什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:21:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,比起勉強梳起來 像現在這樣不也挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.43,0:21:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,想要保持現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,現在必須做出改變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,由良良？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大家辛苦了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什…什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,由良親 你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是由良之助君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我要認真參加生存遊戲！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,再也不會逃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可愛死啦 由良林
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.07,0:21:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,今後會狠狠調教你的哦 由良公
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.99,0:22:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,外號就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.91,0:22:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,今後請大家叫我由良！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,知道啦 由良
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我會加油的！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.78,0:24:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\3c&HF7F7F7&\pos(640,38)\c&H646464&}下集預告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.37,0:23:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,由良的新髮型非常合適呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.77,0:23:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,欸嘿嘿 非常感謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我要不要也剪短呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.95,0:23:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 好可惜 明明有一頭天生的金髮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.61,0:23:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那我剪短好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.84,0:23:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,咦！？小蓮不也有一頭漂亮的長髮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:23:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,又長又柔順 羡慕死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.93,0:23:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然每天都有剪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.90,0:24:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.81,0:24:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 無箭之弓方可制敵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.47,0:24:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,小園呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.46,0:24:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我頭髮不會長哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.49,0:24:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.21,0:24:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:11.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,Command
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:13.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,Control
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:15.42,EDJP,,0,0,0,,Communication
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:16.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,C3！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.30,0:22:17.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.01,0:22:20.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,サバイバルっちゃっても　ガンガン撃って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:22.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,フラッグ取っちゃって　そうバンバン
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:23.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,Hit！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:28.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,笑顔になっちゃって　楽しんでなんぼじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.67,0:22:30.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,,Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.95,0:22:35.10,EDJP,,0,0,0,,仲間とアイコンタクトって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.10,0:22:38.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,照れちゃうんだけど　いいかも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.76,0:22:41.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,信じあって弾けましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.91,0:22:45.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,Ready?　3,2,1 Go,Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:48.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,仲間と目指せフラッグゲット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.44,0:22:52.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,進めば感じるドキドキ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.12,0:22:55.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,当たって弾けましょう　だね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.99,0:22:58.75,EDJP,,0,0,0,,3,2,1 Go,Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.75,0:23:04.79,EDJP,,0,0,0,,悲しいも苦しいも乗り越えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.39,0:23:11.96,EDJP,,0,0,0,,今よりもずっとずっずっと笑顔になる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.96,0:23:13.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,全員、配置につけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.67,0:23:15.37,EDJP,,0,0,0,,ハイ、はい、ハイ、はい、ハイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.37,0:23:18.68,EDJP,,0,0,0,,サバイバルっちゃっても　ガンガン撃って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.68,0:23:21.41,EDJP,,0,0,0,,フラッグ取っちゃって　そうバンバン
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.41,0:23:22.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,Hit！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.01,0:23:27.10,EDJP,,0,0,0,,涙奪っちゃっても　青春　走れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:28.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Bung！ Bung！ Bung！ Fu！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.62,0:23:31.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,以心伝心　一歩前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.90,0:23:35.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,うつむくな前を向け
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:39.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,張り切っちゃってお待たせ
